## üîÑ Workflow ‚Äì End-to-End RAG Pipeline Execution

```python
# 1Ô∏è‚É£ Load PDF documents
from document_loader import load_documents
documents = load_documents("data/")
```

# 2Ô∏è‚É£ Split documents into text chunks
from chunker import split_into_chunks
chunks = split_into_chunks(documents)

# 3Ô∏è‚É£ Generate embeddings and store in FAISS
from embeddings import embed_and_store
embed_and_store(chunks, "faiss_index")

# 4Ô∏è‚É£ Run a query through the RAG pipeline
from rag_pipeline import answer_query

query = "What are the age and salary limits for US Visa Screening?"
response = answer_query(query)

print("LLM Output:")
print(response)
